{"tid":582533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨生子女軍人存「巨嬰心理」　軍媒批上不了戰場","createTime":"2018-03-06T09:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T09:55:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a87e554bc5b6c412c3fa163513147f9c190fe88a","tid":582533,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180306/photo/bkncn-20180306103802456-0306_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180306122941\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180306%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180306103802456-0306_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180306122941&h=ad6c38e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地年輕一代嬌生慣養，從小就在父母的溺愛中成長，成年後仍走不出「衣來伸手、飯來張口」的心態。這種成年人心理滯留在嬰兒水平的情況在內地被稱為「巨嬰心理」，近年愈來愈嚴重而且蔓延到軍營。內地軍媒發文批評，這些獨生子女的年輕軍人自我中心，心理太幼稚、想法太天真，而且經不起磨練，上不了戰場。<br />\n<br />\n文章表示，「巨嬰心理」不是合格戰士的心理特徵。練兵打仗，需要意志堅定、英勇頑強，任何時候都不怕流血犧牲，「巨嬰心理」像花瓶般脆弱，經不起摔打，扛不起重任，上不了戰場，不利於戰鬥集體協同作戰。行軍作戰，講究絕對服從和相互配合，單打獨鬥是大忌。「巨嬰心理」總以自我為中心，執行戰鬥任務時容易影響集體行動。 <br />\n<br />\n文章又指，一個時代的戰士，有一個時代的烙印，「巨嬰心理」就是當今少數獨生子女官兵的時代烙印。這些人從校門直接走進營門，社會經驗缺乏，心理、心智不成熟是共性問題。強調「巨嬰心理」是一種心理疾患，一線帶兵主管要把握住「巨嬰心理」的特質，掌握心理疏導方法，有針對性地開展疏導工作，轉變他們對生活的態度，幫助他們勇敢走向訓練場，挑戰自己、磨礪自己、摔打自己，彌補心理的缺陷，培育他們盡快成長為高質素的軍人。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180306/bkncn-20180306103802456-0306_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180306%2Fbkncn-20180306103802456-0306_05011_001.html&d=AiK%2FvUy3SAFDSmMwJ3%2B86wdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=97742fe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180306/bkncn-20180306103802456-0306_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f3876535f77a69dbe7eb44119e4aee52336bf77c","tid":582533,"uid":71091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:08:19.000Z","msg":"支狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c17708fcee9edeebbdfcebf1781380464c65d0c","tid":582533,"uid":38671,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"元朝末年，曾經好好打既蒙古人經過長年糜爛生活變廢<br />\n<br />\n歷史不斷重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f888debd1e1dc06c46dfbcf75ac8a25c3615ad","tid":582533,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7a32069bb7b8523e1b0b68218ea627d3cc10dab","tid":582533,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73f888debd1e1dc06c46dfbcf75ac8a25c3615ad","tid":582533,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"我覺得剩係叫<del>習太祖</del>主席好就得"},{"pid":"deb83cffc7054689f1fa2fb2bb490876db9c36b1","tid":582533,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"社會主義巨嬰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b022c9e861482aa1992344945386b9eccd040ce2","tid":582533,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b34dbb551a987e40fb3b50e7f339ee134e7012","tid":582533,"uid":126567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b022c9e861482aa1992344945386b9eccd040ce2","tid":582533,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"你個名"},{"pid":"5c507a7c116a4eab5611150ace9a5fe2bf719860","tid":582533,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c17708fcee9edeebbdfcebf1781380464c65d0c","tid":582533,"uid":38671,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20